<p>Appearing on Demi Burnett's Big Demi Energy podcast in August, the ballroom dancing prodigy revealed she turned down the coveted role 'because it didn't feel right'. </p>

<p>'They offered it to me a couple of times actually because I judge Dancing with the Stars in Australia,' she explained.</p>

<p>'I considered it long and hard and thought about it, but it didn't feel right for me.' </p>

